summary: This mod adds the swimming suit for an athlete.
descriptionHtml:
Name:Competition Swimsuit -CBBE
Version: 1.1
Date: 2013/09/10
by Shimaneko
-------------------[ Description ]-----------------------
This mod adds to the game competition swimsuits for CBBE body.
The base body was made by \"BodySlide.exe\".
It supports the weight slider.
These are registered as Light Armor.

How to get: 
Uses leather at the tanning rack.
It upgrades using a leather strips. 

-------------------[ Credit ]------------------------
Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE-
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666/


-------------------[ Change History ]------------------------
2013/08/20 v1.0 Initial release
2013/09/10 v1.1 Mesh changed
By a weight slider,a breast becomes large.
